cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is focused on teaching artificial agents to use natural language through human-in-the-loop training. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses machine learning methods for training artificial agents. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper investigates the relationship between different learning signals and their impact on sample efficiency. 
4. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper investigates S2P schedules in an image-based referential game. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper introduces population-based approaches to S2P, which could be relevant to systems and control.
